Definition: Muslim schools in Bangladesh and Pakistan
Example: the Pakistan government decided to close down madrasas that provided military training for their students; many madrasas in Bangladesh are supported with money from Saudi Arabia
Synonyms: madrasah, religious_school, noun, location, Bangladesh, r, Pakistan, Muslim, schools, in, and, the, government, decided, to, close, down, madrasas, that, provided, military, training, for, their, students, many, are, supported, with, money, from, Saudi, Arabia
Category: noun.group
